entries.title_d: The Empire had some of their elite TIE Interceptors shadow their spy in case any complications came up. They are set on your destruction, surprise them by fighting back and show them that the Alliance have no fear!
entries.title: Dathomir system: Defeat the elite TIE squadron.
entries.split_quest_alert: Rebel Command: < You impress me pilot. Let's keep this winning streak going with another attack where it hurts the Empire the most. Proceed to the Dantooine system for further instructions. >
entries.complete: You have survived the Suprise Attack!
